@startuml
|User|
start
: (1) Click on Add button in Manage supplier screen;
|System|
: (2) Display form to create new Supplier;
|User|
repeat: (3) Fill supplier information;
: (4) Click on Confirm button;
|System|
: (5) Validate supplier information;
backward: (6) Show error message;
repeat while (Information valid?) is (no) not (yes)
: (7) Add new Supplier to the database;
: (8) Update Manage supplier screen;
stop
@enduml
